{
  "texts": [
    "It consists of 19,150 entities and 4,365 relation pairs.",
    "The primary focus of this dataset is to gauge LLMs' proficiency in tasks related to NER and RE within the field of classical Chinese language studies.",
    "The assessment methodology is grounded in code-based evaluations.",
    "• C-Eval (Huang et al, 2023c).",
    "The C-Eval dataset comprises 13,948 Chinese multiple-choice questions, spanning 52 different academic disciplines and categorized into four difficulty levels."
  ]
}